data.description: Are you looking for home with acreage? Then don’t pass up the opportunity to see this property! This impressive home sits on 6.76 fenced in acres that includes a barn, corrals and pens with pipe fencing, chicken pen and electronic gates. The minute you walk in the front door you’ll see a wide-open layout with excellent natural lighting. The vaulted wood oak plank ceiling is gorgeous and the flooring is Acai wood plank throughout the living areas and bedrooms. The Master Bedroom is large with a connecting ensuite that includes a separate shower, jet tub and walk-in closet. The other bedrooms are nice sized with large closets. The kitchen is spacious with a lot of cabinets for storage. An Extra Feature you're going to love is the Reverse Osmosis water system that provides great tasting drinking water. Don’t just stop with looking at the pictures but let them entice you to come see this home! You'll be glad you did!!
